th your consideration, Twiggie.<br>
<br>
Here is my tought.<br>
<br>
First of all, i don't hope any &quot;exception&quot; in common rule basicaly,even if it is good for us.<br>
Your suggestion is one of choice for solution,<br>
but the complicated rule only for one guild, will make this reservation rule more complicated.<br>
Sooner of later it will be like cheese with bunch of gaping hole in Tom and Jelly.<br>
Rule must be strict and simple.<br>
<br>
There are mainly only 2 problems on current rule for me.<br>
1.Rule asks to reserve &quot;DATE&quot;<br>
2.Because of time difference plane will be wasted between USA and Asian raids.<br>
<br>
Problem1,<br>
If rule allows us to have shift to next &quot;date&quot; and have few hours delay, this will be solve very simply, for us.<br>
Someone suggested 24x14 hours reservation instead of 14days one.<br>
This reservation of &quot;DATE&quot; is causing us troubule tho,<br>
on the other hand it gives everyone fair chance imo.<br>
If it becomes 24x14 hours rule, board camp will be much worse<br>
and ppl will try to reserve plane as early as possible<br>
even tho they can't make the time.<br>
So i support current 14days rule.<br>
<br>
Problem2,<br>
This is the main reason many ppl are flaming me about.<br>
In this case, FoH raids fear 20th 5pm PST.<br>
It will be respawn at 21th 7am PST.<br>
Zenith will raid fear 22th 5am PST.<br>
Here is 22 hours &quot;dead&quot; time between Zenith and FoH.<br>
USA ppl can't raid in this 22 hours, so it is &quot;dead&quot; time.<br>
After Zenith raid fear will respawn at 22th 7pm PST.<br>
This is ideal number, i think this time is hard for USA ppl to start raid from,<br>
so think it that USA ppl need to make plan on 23th 5pm PST.<br>
Here is another 22 hours dead time.<br>
Total, 44 hours &quot;waste&quot; we will have.<br>
<br>
If that is only for USA ppl,<br>
Guild A starts raid from 20th 5pm PST.<br>
Fear repops at 21th 7am PST.<br>
Guild B starts raid from 21th 5pm PST<br>
There is only 10 hours dead time, and it is good enough for margin to adjust spawn cycle.<br>
<br>
Our time based reservation is, 2 days monopolization FOR USA ppl.<br>
Even if it is 1 day raid for us.<br>
And most of ppl don't wish that, so trying to prevent asian/european raids.<br>
There is no solution without working out by each side of ppl.<br>
I wish this thread leads us to one answer.<br>
<br>
&gt;I don't see him risking losing his one chance a month to have<br>
&gt;a full raid by taking a Tuesday or Wednesday. From every<br>
&gt;post I've seen Roatus make he's looking for armor mobs, NOT<br>
&gt;epic mobs. <br>
<br>
I want to get some armors for young ppl tho,<br>
our main purpose is epic pieces.<br>
Probably you saw our sign up board and saw many ppl who are under 50th and no plane armors.<br>
Many lazy slackers (zenith members) still haven't signed up yet.<br>
Our guild average level is 58.8<br>
here is our member list<br>
